message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Federated Agent Audit: Privacy auditing for multi-agent AI systems"
abstract: >-
  A privacy-preserving audit framework for multi-agent AI systems that detects
  compositional privacy leaks (cross-domain flows, aggregation/inference,
  cascading injection) across agent interactions without the central auditor
  ever accessing raw content.
